/original/db0e350dc2827fb0.png" alt="Mastodon image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111743631692767349</guid><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 15:15:05 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Manlio De Domenico</title><link>https://mathstodon.xyz/@manlius/111744238092534983</link><description>üö®&lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mathstodon.xyz/tags/ComplexityThoughts" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;ComplexityThoughts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; issue #24: &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mathstodon.xyz/tags/ComplexSystems" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;ComplexSystems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mathstodon.xyz/tags/NetworkScience" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;NetworkScience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mathstodon.xyz/tags/Neuroscience" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Neuroscience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mathstodon.xyz/tags/HumanBehavior" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;HumanBehavior&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mathstodon.xyz/tags/Evolution" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Evolution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Unraveling complexity: building knowledge, one paper at a time! &lt;br/&gt;Not yet subscribed? It's never too late, and it's 100% free.&lt;a href="https://open.substack.com/pub/manlius/p/complexity-thoughts-issue-24?r=n4iyo&amp;amp;utm_campaign=post&amp;amp;utm_medium=web&amp;amp;showWelcome=true" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;open.substack.com/pub/manlius/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;p/complexity-thoughts-issue-24?r=n4iyo&amp;amp;utm_campaig